          <long_desc isprivate="0">
            <commentid>1645</commentid>
            <who name="Sebastian Werner">info</who>
            <bug_when>2007-06-26 16:29:58 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>This seems to be related to the zone managment system. There is also a knowledge-base entry available at Microsoft&#39;s support page:

http://support.microsoft.com/?scid=kb%3Ben-us%3B934366



</thetext>
          </long_desc>
          <long_desc isprivate="0">
            <commentid>1646</commentid>
            <who name="Sebastian Werner">info</who>
            <bug_when>2007-06-26 16:32:33 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>Not a qooxdoo bug but an issue with Microsoft&#39;s new security zone managment.

If this occurs in qooxdoo applications try to re-execute &quot;make&quot; or &quot;make build&quot;.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
